    "details": {
      "description": "<p>The kyokor unleashes a terrible roar.</p><hr /><p>When a kyokor passes by or through a settlement—or even attacks!—it leaves a trail of destruction that can be represented by the following hazards.</p><hr /><p>Terrifying, skyscraper-sized beasts roam the wastelands of Daimalko. Called colossi by the population, these monsters erupted from deep within the earth to stomp cities into dust, decimating the population and destroying every surface civilization on the planet in a terrifying Awakening. Kyokors are among the most dreaded colossi. There's no hope of defeating one without a valko—a war machine created by Daimalko's stubborn survivors to fight the colossi.</p>",
      "level": {
        "value": 20
      },
      "isComplex": false,
      "disable": "<p>@Check[arcana|dc:50] (legendary), @Check[occultism|dc:50] (legendary), or @Check[performance|dc:50] (legendary) to counteract the roar</p>",
      "routine": "",
      "reset": "<p>The kyokor must wait [[/gmr 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds} before roaring again.</p>",
